# Day 3 - AWS Billing Metrics & Budget Alerts

## Situation
To ensure cost control and avoid unexpected charges while building the cloud project.

## Task
Enable AWS billing metrics and set up a budget alert.

## Actions
- Enabled Cost Explorer in AWS Billing Preferences.
- Activated Billing Alerts and Billing Metrics in CloudWatch (N. Virginia region).
- Created a budget of $5/month with email alerts at 80% and 100% usage.
- Verified EstimatedCharges metric in CloudWatch.

## Results
- Real-time cost tracking enabled.
- Alerts set to prevent exceeding free-tier usage.
- Project is now protected from unexpected billing.

## Tools Used
- AWS Billing
- AWS Cost Explorer
- AWS CloudWatch
